      423.7,
      527.22,
      437.7
    ],
    "text": "1. The Accused-Appellant (hereinafter referred to as the Appellant) has",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      438.82,
      527.13,
      513.8
    ],
    "text": "been indicted in the High Court of Colombo in High Court case number 591/19. 2. The charges in the indictment as follows;",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style",
      "Bookman Old Style,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      128.69,
      530.04,
      501.27,
      711.37
    ],
    "text": "Charge 01 That on or about June 22,2017, within the jurisdiction of this Court, you did possess 01.56 grams of heroin, an offence punishable in terms of section 54A(d) of the Poisons, Opium and Dangerous Drugs Ordinance (as amended by Act No.13 of 1984). Charge 02 That during the course of the same transaction, you did traffic 01.56 grams of heroin, an offence punishable in terms of section 54A(b) of the Poisons, Opium and Dangerous Drugs Ordinance (as amended by Act No. 13 of 1984).",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      782.02,
      324.94,
      806.26
    ],
    "text": "Page 3 of 4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      71.76,
      526.95,
      85.76
    ],
    "text": "3. At the conclusion of the trial, the Learned High Court Judge has",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      86.88,
      527.22,
      131.36
    ],
    "text": "convicted the appellant of the charges in the indictment, sentenced the appellant as follows;",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      128.69,
      132.51,
      501.25,
      268.21
    ],
    "text": "Charge 01 A term of 7 years rigorous imprisonment and also imposed a fine of Rs.100,000.00 with a term of one-year simple imprisonment, in default. Charge 02 A term of 7 years rigorous imprisonment and also imposed a fine of Rs.100,000.00 with a term of one year simple imprisonment, in default.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      300.56,
      527.2,
      314.56
    ],
    "text": "4. Aggrieved by the conviction, the disputed judgment and the sentencing",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      315.92,
      507.07,
      329.92
    ],
    "text": "order, the appellant has preferred the instant appeal to this Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      362.24,
      527.22,
      376.24
    ],
    "text": "5. When the matter was taken up for argument, the learned counsel for",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      377.36,
      527.18,
      436.98
    ],
    "text": "the appellant informed Court that the appellant did not wish to contest the conviction but only the sentencing order. Accordingly, the following ground of appeal was urged by the Learned Counsel for the appellant;",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      135.89,
      438.34,
      486.94,
      467.46
    ],
    "text": "i. Are the sentences imposed on the appellant disproportionate?",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      499.8,
      526.96,
      513.8
    ],
    "text": "6. The law at the time the indictment was forwarded has mandated a",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      515.16,
      528.67,
      544.28
    ],
    "text": "specific penalty for the offences for which the appellant was convicted.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      128.69,
      545.4,
      500.87,
      635.57
    ],
    "text": "The penalty was as follows; fine not less than one hundred thousand rupees and not exceeding five hundred thousand rupees and imprisonment of either description for a period not less than seven years and not exceeding twenty years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style",
      "Bookman Old Style,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      668.09,
      526.96,
      727.69
    ],
    "text": "The Learned High Court Judge has thoroughly considered this legal framework, along with the pertinent facts presented in mitigation.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      782.02,
      324.94,
      806.26
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      71.76,
      527.13,
      85.76
    ],
    "text": "7. While the Learned Counsel for the appellant has submitted a request",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      86.88,
      531.07,
      161.87
    ],
    "text": "in the High Court for a non-custodial sentence, he has not sufficiently elaborated on the reasons or the circumstances in support of such plea. 8. Nonetheless, the Learned High Court Judge has taken into account",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style",
      "Bookman Old Style,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      162.99,
      527.0,
      344.32
    ],
    "text": "several significant factors including the appellants age i.e. he is a sixty-five-year-old male and his role as the sole breadwinner for his family, which includes two children. In the light of these considerations, the disputed sentencing order has been made after a comprehensive review of all relevant facts presented to the Learned High Court Judge. 9. This Court remains mindful of the legal obligations imposed by the",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      82.34,
      345.44,
      527.23,
      435.54
    ],
    "text": "mandatory sentencing laws, while also weighing the personal circumstances of the appellant considering a balanced approach to justice. 10. In those circumstances, this Court is not inclined to interfere with the",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      100.37,
      436.66,
      472.97,
      450.72
    ],
    "text": "disputed sentencing order. Therefore, the appeal is dismissed.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style",
      "Bookman Old Style,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.05,
      467.14,
      321.96,
      496.34
    ],
    "text": "I make no order regarding costs.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style,Italic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      82.34,
      497.66,
      527.07,
      516.68
    ],
    "text": "11. However, the substantial terms of rigorous imprisonment of 7 years",
    "fonts": [
      "Arial",
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      100.37,
      517.8,
      527.23,
      562.28
    ],
    "text": "each, shall commence from the date of conviction, i.e., September 06, 2023, and run concurrently.",
    "fonts": [
      "Bookman Old Style"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
